This is the software that runs the BEACON station. 
It depends on libbeacon for talking to the boards. 

It consists of several programs: 

beacon-acq:   Data Acquisition (beacon-acq.c)
beacon-copy:  Data copying to beacon-archive (beacon-copy.c)
beacon-hk:   Housekeeping  / power control daemon     (beacon-hk.c)
beacon-startup: Startup process that does basically nothing in beacon. (beacon-startup.c) 



Influential environmental variables: 

  BEACON_CONFIG_DIR : defines the directory to read config files from 
  


